{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/projects/word-clock","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I followed instructions from Make magazine (Volume 67) and made word clock.</p>\n<p>I also started a <a href=\"https://repl.it/@stakanmartini/WordClock#main.cpp\">code project</a> discovering ways to combine words into a grid.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/3acf0/word-clock-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Acryl is ready\"\n        title=\"Acryl is ready\"\n        src=\"/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/4b190/word-clock-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/e07e9/word-clock-1.jpg 200w,\n/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/066f9/word-clock-1.jpg 400w,\n/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/4b190/word-clock-1.jpg 800w,\n/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/e5166/word-clock-1.jpg 1200w,\n/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/b17f8/word-clock-1.jpg 1600w,\n/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/3acf0/word-clock-1.jpg 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Why</h2>\n<p>It will stay on the table and will show time when I need to head out of the office.</p>\n<h2>Process</h2>\n<p>Ordered laser cut, bought screws and adafruit boards.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/3acf0/word-clock-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Peel it\"\n        title=\"Peel it\"\n        src=\"/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/4b190/word-clock-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/e07e9/word-clock-2.jpg 200w,\n/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/066f9/word-clock-2.jpg 400w,\n/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/4b190/word-clock-2.jpg 800w,\n/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/e5166/word-clock-2.jpg 1200w,\n/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/b17f8/word-clock-2.jpg 1600w,\n/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/3acf0/word-clock-2.jpg 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>How do you call screen that does not display time with digits, but tells it with words?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/3acf0/word-clock-3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"The case\"\n        title=\"The case\"\n        src=\"/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/4b190/word-clock-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/e07e9/word-clock-3.jpg 200w,\n/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/066f9/word-clock-3.jpg 400w,\n/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/4b190/word-clock-3.jpg 800w,\n/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/e5166/word-clock-3.jpg 1200w,\n/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/b17f8/word-clock-3.jpg 1600w,\n/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/3acf0/word-clock-3.jpg 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Result</h2>\n<p>The clock is working. I will edit video of the process soon.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"May 16, 2020","path":"/projects/word-clock","title":"Word clock","draft":null,"subtitle":null,"buttonText":null,"buttonLink":null,"featuredImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"showLikes":true,"pagePath":"/projects/word-clock","breadcrumb":{"location":"/projects/word-clock","crumbs":[{"pathname":"/","crumbLabel":"Index"},{"pathname":"/projects","crumbLabel":"projects"},{"pathname":"/projects/word-clock","crumbLabel":"word-clock"}]}}}}